thi F.C.|Skoda Xanthi]]</small> |position=left}}\n}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n! Team\n! Manager<sup>1</sup>\n! Location\n! Stadium\n! Capacity\n|-\n| [[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]\n| {{flagicon|POR}} [[Fernando Santos (Portuguese footballer)|Fernando Santos]]\n| [[Athens]]\n| [[Olympic Stadium (Athens)|Athens Olympic Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 71,030\n|-\n| [[Apollon Pontou FC|Apollon Kalamarias]] \n| {{flagicon|SCG}} [[Dragan Kokotovi\u0107]]\n| [[Thessaloniki]]\n| [[Kalamaria Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 6,500\n|-\n| [[Aris Thessaloniki F.C.|Aris]]\n| {{flagicon|GRE}} [[Georgios Chatzaras]]\n| [[Thessaloniki]]\n| [[Kleanthis Vikelidis Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 23,220\n|-\n| [[Chalkidona F.C.|Chalkidona]]\n| {{flagicon|GRE}} [[Georgios Paraschos]]\n| [[Athens]]\n| [[Peristeri Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 9,035\n|-\n| [[Egaleo F.C.|Egaleo]]\n| {{flagicon|ROM}} [[Ilie Dumitrescu]]\n| [[Athens]]\n| [[Stavros Mavrothalassitis Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 8,217\n|-\n| [[Ergotelis F.C.|Ergotelis]]\n| {{flagicon|GRE}} Manolis Patmetzis\n| [[Heraklion]]\n| [[Pankritio Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 26,400\n|-\n| [[Ionikos F.C.|Ionikos]]\n| {{flagicon|GRE}} [[Vangelis Vlachos]]\n| [[Piraeus]]\n| [[Neapoli Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 4,999\n|-\n| [[Iraklis 1908 Thessaloniki F.C.|Iraklis]]\n| {{flagicon|URU}} [[Sergio Markari\u00e1n]]\n| [[Thessaloniki]]\n| [[Kaftanzoglio Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 27,770\n|-\n| [[Kallithea F.C.|Kallithea]]\n| {{flagicon|GRE}} [[Takis Lemonis]]\n| [[Kallithea]]\n| [[Grigoris Lambrakis Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 4,250\n|-\n| [[PAE Kerkyra|Kerkyra]]\n| {{flagicon|GRE}} [[Lakis Papaioannou]]\n| [[Corfu (city)|Corfu]]\n| [[Kerkyra Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 2,685\n|-\n| [[OFI Crete F.C.|OFI]]\n| {{flagicon|GRE}} [[Giannis Chatzinikolaou]]\n| [[Heraklion]]\n| [[Theodoros Vardinogiannis Stadium]]\n| align=\"center\" | 9,000\n|-\n| [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n| {