ory:Balinese people]]\n[[Category:Anugerah Musik Indonesia winners]]\n", "text_old": "{{about|the Indonesian-German actress and singer|her self-titled debut album released in 2010|Cinta Laura (album)}}\n{{short description|Indonesian-German singer, actress and model}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Cinta Laura\n| image              = \n| birth_name         = Cinta Laura Kiehl\n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|1993|08|17|df=y}}\n| birth_place        = [[Quakenbr\u00fcck]], [[Lower Saxony]], Germany\n| alma_mater         = [[Columbia University]]<br>[[Jakarta International School]]\n| occupation         = {{Hlist|Singer|Actress|Dancer|Businesswomen|Model|former National Swimmer}}\n| home_town          = \n| nationality        = [[German people|German]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnnindonesia.com/hiburan/20160815213400-234-151571/affidavit-dokumen-wn-ganda-penyelamat-cinta-laura|title=Affidavit, Dokumen WN Ganda 'Penyelamat' Cinta Laura|author=Rizky Sekar Afrisia|work=CNN Indonesia|language=id|access-date=21 April 2020|date=15 August 2016|quote=...Dan bintang The Philosophers itu memilih Jerman....}}</ref>\n| height             = {{height|m=1.74}}<ref name=\"auto10\">{{cite web|url=https://influencer-dic.com/cinta-laura-kiehl-bio-weight-height-age-social-media-tv-shows-wiki-facts/|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl Bio, Weight, Height, Age, Social Media, TV Shows, Wiki, Facts|language=English|publisher=American Influencer Dictionary|year=2019|accessdate=April 30, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.voaindonesia.com/a/cinta-laura-raih-2-gelar-sarjana-dengan-cum-laude/1924508.html|title=Cinta Laura Raih 2 Gelar Sarjana dengan Predikat Cum Laude|trans-title=Cinta Laura Got 2 Bachelor's Degrees with Cum Laude Predicate|language=Indonesian|publisher=VOA Indonesia|year=2014|accessdate=September 29, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.charmboard.com/en/scene/cinta-laura-kiehl-cast-in-vida-cinta-laura-kiehl-2019/p/cbve3mPzLXXon-1596845|language=English|title=Featuring Cinta Laura Kiehl as Lead Artiste|publisher=charmboard.com|year=2011|accessdate=September 29, 2011}}</ref>\n| module             = {{Infobox musical artist|embed=yes\n| background = solo_singer\n| instrument = Vocals\n| Genre = Pop Music, electropop, hip hop, dance music\n| years_active = 2007\u2013present\n| label = [[Sony Music Entertainment]]\n| website = {{URL|www.cintalaurakiehl-clk.com}}\n<!-- Do not weasel in a signature here, a parameter for signatures does not exist for a reason -->\n}}\n}}\n\n'''Cinta Laura Kiehl''', better known as '''Cinta Laura''' ({{IPA-id|\u02c8t\u0283inta \u02c8laura|lang}}; {{IPA-de|\u02c8t\u0283i\u02d0n'ta 'la\u028a\u0281a|lang}} born 17 August 1993), is an [[German people|German]]-[[Indonesians|Indonesian]] actress, [[electropop]] singer and model in [[Indonesia]].<ref name=\"auto7\">{{cite web|url=https://tvshowstars.com/cinta-laura-bio-age-height-career-boyfriend-net-worth/|title=Cinta Laura Biography- Age, Height, Career, Boyfriend, Net Worth|language=English|publisher=tvshowstars.com|year=2007|accessdate=July 19, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://today.line.me/id/pc/article/Indonesian+actress+Cinta+Laura+accused+of+insensitivity+over+tweet+asking+students+to+stop+protesting-krKXRk|title=Indonesian actress Cinta Laura accused of insensitivity over tweet asking students to stop protesting|language=English|publisher=today.line.me|year=2019|accessdate=October 2, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.last.fm/music/Cinta+Laura/+wiki|title=Cinta Laura Biography|language=English|publisher=Blogseleb.com|year=2011|accessdate=March 21, 2011}}</ref> She was recently appointed ambassador of [[anti-violence]] against women and children by the [[Ministry of Women Empowerment and Child Protection|Indonesian Ministry of Women Empowerment and Child Protection]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://colours-indonesia.com/en/lifestyle/interview/cinta-laura-kiehl-2/|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl : Vision for Women\u2019s Rights|language=English|publisher=Garuda Indonesia Magazine|year=2019|accessdate=January 1, 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Early life and background ==\nLaura was born on 17 August 1993 in [[Quakenbr\u00fcck]], [[Lower Saxony]], [[Germany]]. Her father, Michael Kiehl, was a [[Germans|German]] hotelier, and her mother, Herdiana Soekarseno, was an [[Indonesia]]n lawyer of ethnic [[Sundanese people|Sundanese]] and [[Balinese people|Balinese]] descent.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.celebsfacts.com/cinta-laura/|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl Family & Biography|language=English|publisher=celebsfacts.com|year=2009|accessdate=19 May 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.famousdetails.com/cinta-laura/|title=Cinta Laura: Top 10 Must-Know Facts About Pop Singer|language=English|publisher=famousdetails.com|year=2017|accessdate=30 December 2017}}</ref> Due to her father\u2019s job, Laura grew up in several countries such as the [[United Arab Emirates|UAE]], [[Saudi Arabia]], [[Malaysia]], [[Singapore]], [[Germany]] and [[Indonesia]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.prestigeonline.com/id/people-events/quality-time-paris-cinta-laura/|title=Quality Time in Paris with Cinta Laura|language=English|publisher=prestigeonline.com|year=2017|accessdate=16 November 2017}}</ref> which led her to grow up with [[English language|English]], [[Indonesians|Indonesian]] and [[Germans|German]] as her language.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvshowstars.com/cinta-laura-bio-age-height-career-boyfriend-net-worth/|title=Cinta Laura Biography- Age, Height, Career, Boyfriend, Net Worth|language=English|publisher=tvshowstars.com|year=2007|accessdate=19 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.datingcelebs.com/who-is-cinta-laura-dating/|title=Who is Cinta Laura Dating Now?|language=en|publisher=datingcelebs.com|year=2019|accessdate=28 December 2019}}</ref> Upon her move to [[Indonesia]] at 12 years old, Laura become an Indonesia's national [[swimmer]], she won 10 gold medals, 7 silver medals and 7 bronze medals from various swimming competition.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rmolbanten.com/read/2018/08/30/2781/Cinta-Laura,-Raih-10-Medali-Emas-Di-Kolam-Renang-|title=Cinta Laura, Raih 10 Medali Emas Di Kolam Renang|trans-title=\nCinta Laura, Won 10 Gold Medals in Swimming Competition|language=Indonesian|publisher=rmolbanten.com|year=2018|accessdate=30 August 2018}}</ref>\n\nLaura attain a great success at [[Columbia University]], [[New York City]], allowing her to graduate a year earlier than expected.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indonesiatatler.com/fashion-beauty/fashion/it-looks-cinta-laura-kiehl-s-10-most-photogenic-looks|title=IT Looks: Cinta Laura Kiehl\u2019s 10 Most Photogenic Looks|language=en|publisher=indonesiatatler.com|year=2017|accessdate=11 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hotcourses.co.id/study-in-usa/university-applications/suka-duka-kuliah-di-amerika-cinta-laura/|title=Suka Duka Kuliah Di AMerika Serikat, Cinta Laura|trans-title=Love and Joy of University Life's in the United States, Cinta Laura|language=Indonesian|publisher=hotcourses.co.id|year=2016|accessdate=21 November 2016}}</ref> She is also a teaching assistant (TA) for Professor [[Herbert S. Terrace]] in Columbia\u2019s psychology department.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indonesiatatler.com/fashion-beauty/fashion/it-looks-cinta-laura-kiehl-s-10-most-photogenic-looks|title=IT Looks: Cinta Laura Kiehl\u2019s 10 Most Photogenic Looks|language=English|publisher=indonesiatatler.com|year=2017|accessdate=11 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.okezone.com/read/2014/06/04/373/993934/selama-kuliah-cinta-laura-jadi-asisten-dosen-psikologi|title=Selama Kuliah, Cinta Laura Jadi Asisten Dosen Psikologi|trans-title=During her studies, Cinta Laura became an Teaching Assistant Lecturer in Psychology|language=Indonesian|publisher=okezone.com Indonesia|year=2014|accessdate=4 June 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://video.tribunnews.com/view/85754/cinta-laura-aktris-indonesia|title=Cinta Laura - Aktris Indonesia, kuliah di Amerika Serikat|trans-title=Cinta Laura, Indonesian Actress, Studying in United States|language=Indonesian|publisher=okezone.com Indonesia|year=2019|accessdate=6 July 2019}}</ref> While at Columbia, she joined the sorority [[Kappa Alpha Theta]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kappaalphatheta.org/heritage/notable-thetas|title=Notable Thetas|language=English|publisher=kappaalphatheta.org|year=2012|accessdate=10 February 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wowkeren.com/foto/seleb/cinta-laura/cinta-laura-instagram-05.html|title=Foto Cinta Laura Bersama Ketua Kappa Alpha Theta|trans-title=Cinta Laura Photos During Kappa Alpha Tetta with The Board of Chairman|language=Indonesian|publisher=wowkeren.com|year=2012|accessdate=20 January 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/xcintakiehlx/status/168027814010945536?lang=en|title=Kappa Alpha Theta!|language=english|publisher=xcintakiehlx|year=2012|accessdate=10 February 2012}}</ref> Laura graduated [[cum laude]] from the university in May 2014.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.voaindonesia.com/a/cinta-laura-raih-2-gelar-sarjana-dengan-cum-laude/1924508.html|title=Cinta Laura Raih 2 Gelar Sarjana dengan Predikat Cum Laude|trans-title=Cinta Laura Got 2 Bachelor's Degrees with Cum Laude Predicate|language=Indonesian|publisher=VOA Indonesia|year=2014|accessdate=29 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.charmboard.com/en/scene/cinta-laura-kiehl-cast-in-vida-cinta-laura-kiehl-2019/p/cbve3mPzLXXon-1596845|language=english|title=Featuring Cinta Laura Kiehl as Lead Artiste|publisher=charmboard.com|year=2011|accessdate=29 September 2011}}</ref> Additionally, after graduate she move to [[Los Angeles]] in order to pursue her acting career in [[Hollywood]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.netralnews.com/news/currentnews/read/7561/cinta.laura.secures.main.role.in.hollywood.movie|title=Cinta Laura Secures Main Role in Hollywood Movie|publisher=netralnews.com|year=2017|accessdate=30 June 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thejakartapost.com/life/2017/12/11/cinta-lauras-hollywood-films-to-premiere-next-year.html|title=Cinta Laura\u2019s Hollywood films to premiere next year|publisher=thejakartapost.com|year=2017|accessdate=11 December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://beritahati.com/en/berita/11314/Cinta-Laura-Will-Play-in-Two-Hollywood-Film-Title|title=Cinta Laura Will Play in Two Hollywood Film Title|publisher=beritahati.com|year=2016|accessdate=20 March 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://jakartaglobe.id/news/indonesian-actress-cinta-laura-lands-role-harry-potter-spin-off|title=Indonesian Actress Cinta Laura Lands Role in 'Harry Potter' Spin-Off|language=en|publisher=jakartaglobe.id|year=2015|accessdate=28 December 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidehook.com/article/arts-entertainment/meet-cinta-laura-maxim-indonesias-latest-cover-girl|title=Meet Cinta Laura, Maxim Indonesia\u2019s Latest Cover Girl, Who\u2019s Out to Conquer Hollywood|language=en |publisher=daman.co.id|year=2017|accessdate=5 January 2017}}</ref> signing her contract under [[Netflix]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.industry.co.id/read/5774/more-success-cinta-laura-starring-netflix-production-movies|title=More Success, Cinta Laura Starring Netflix Production Movies|language=English|publisher=industry.co.id|year=2018|accessdate=3 June 2018}}</ref> and [[Grindstone Entertainment Group]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/berlin-grindstone-picks-up-ninth-passenger-north-america-1085825|title=Berlin: Grindstone Entertainment Group Picks Up 'Ninth Passenger' for North America (Exclusive)|language=English|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|year=2018|accessdate=17 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://daman.co.id/cinta-laura-embraces-a-new-look-career-and-life-in-hollywood/2/|title=Cinta Laura Embraces A New Look, Career And Life In Hollywood|language=English|publisher=daman.co.id|year=2017|accessdate=9 February 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Acting and singing career==\n===2007: Debut===\nLaura started her career in February 2007, debuted under [[MD Entertainment]]. Her first [[soap opera]], ''[[Cinderella: Apakah Cinta Hanyalah Mimpi?]]'' aired on [[SCTV (Indonesia)|SCTV]] and [[TV2 (Malaysia)]] with 310 episodes,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://daman.co.id/cinta-laura-unveiled-exclusive/|title=Cinta Laura: Unveiled & Exclusive|language=English|publisher=daman.co.id|year=2010|accessdate=17 December 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://theparrot.co/2015/04/09/eurasians-take-show-business-by-storm-in-indonesia/|title=Indonesian showbiz magnet for Eurasians|language=English|publisher=theparrot.co|year=2015|accessdate=9 April 2015}}</ref> where she gain popularity and won ''\u201d2007 Indonesia's Best Actress\u201d'' on [[SCTV Awards|2007 SCTV Awards]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://influencer-dic.com/cinta-laura-kiehl-bio-weight-height-age-social-media-tv-shows-wiki-facts/|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl Bio, Weight, Height, Age, Social Media, TV Shows, Wiki, Facts|language=English|publisher=American Influencer Dictionary|year=2019|accessdate=30 April 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.last.fm/music/Cinta+Laura/+wiki|title=Cinta Laura Biography|language=English|publisher=Blogseleb.com|year=2011|accessdate=21 March  2011}}</ref>\n\n===2007\u22122012: ''Oh Baby'', ''Cinta Laura'' album, and ''Hollywood Dreams''===\n{{listen\n|title       = \"Cinta Atau Uang\"\n|filename    = Cinta Laura - Cinta Atau Uang.ogg\n|description = \"Cinta Atau Uang\" is an [[electropop]] single from the [[Cinta Laura (album)]] and won the [[AMI Awards 2011|Indonesia Music Awards 2011]] for \"Best Dance/Dance Electronic\".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.infospesial.com/news/music/nominasi-anugerah-musik-indonesia-ami-awards-2011.htm|title=Nominasi Anugerah Musik Indonesia AMI Awards 2011|trans-title=Winners of Indonesia Music Awards 2011|language=Indonesian|publisher=Infospesial.com|date=June 18, 2011|accessdate=July 3, 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110621065415/http://www.infospesial.com/news/music/nominasi-anugerah-musik-indonesia-ami-awards-2011.htm|archive-date=June 21, 2011|url-status=dead}}</ref>}}\n\nIn 2007, Laura playing her first movie ''[[:id:Oh Baby|Oh Baby]]'', where she also taking part on the film soundtrack, ''Oh Baby'' reigned in the no. 1 position of various charts in [[Indonesia]], [[Malaysia]] and [[Brunei Darussalam]].<ref name=\"auto1\">{{cite web|url=https://kumparan.com/kumparanhits/transformasi-cinta-laura-dari-oh-baby-hingga-nanny-surveillance-27431110790543034|title=Transformasi Cinta Laura: dari 'Oh Baby' Hingga 'Nanny Surveillance'|trans-title=Cinta Laura Transformation: From 'Oh Baby' until 'Nanny Surveillance'|language=Indonesian|publisher=kumparan.com|year=2018|accessdate=July 11, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3073947/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm|language=English|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl Biography|publisher=imdb official|year=2011|accessdate=November 20, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://celebrity.okezone.com/read/2010/12/23/206/406576/cinta-laura-tolak-film-berbikini|title=Cinta Laura Tolak Film Berbikini|trans-title=Cinta Laura Declined Acting With Bikini|language=Indonesian|publisher=Okezone.com|date=2010-12-23|accessdate=2011-03-20}}</ref> Soon after that, she released her first self-titled studio album, ''[[Cinta Laura (album)|Cinta Laura]] (2010)''.<ref name=\"auto14\">{{cite web|url=http://www.kapanlagi.com/showbiz/selebriti/27-februari-cinta-luncurkan-album-perdana.html|title=27 Februari, Cinta Laura Luncurkan Album Perdana|trans-title=February 27th, Cinta Laura released Her 1st Album|language=Indonesian|publisher=kapanlagi.com|year=2010|accessdate=February 27, 2010}}</ref> The album was released in February 2010 and sold over a million copies.<ref name=\"auto11\">{{cite web|url=http://swa.co.id/listed-articles/nyaringnya-penjualan-album-langsung|title=Nyaringnya Penjualan Album Langsung|trans-title=The loudness of Direct Album Sales|language=Indonesian|publisher=swa.co.id|accessdate=December 12, 2010}}</ref> In the summer of 2010, Cinta received the Wannabe Artist Award of 2010 [[Nickelodeon Indonesia Kids' Choice Awards]].<ref name=\"auto20\">{{cite web|url=https://www.last.fm/music/Cinta+Laura/+wiki|title=Cinta Laura|language=English|publisher=Blogseleb.com|year=2011|accessdate=March 21, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.prestigeonline.com/id/people-events/quality-time-paris-cinta-laura/|title=Quality Time in Paris with Cinta Laura|language=English|publisher=prestigeonline.com|year=2017|accessdate=November 16, 2017}}</ref>\n\nShe also filming her [[soap opera|TV soap series]], ''Upik Abu dan Laura (2008)'' and ''Air Mata Cinta (2009)'', which was a tremendous success in [[Indonesia]] and [[Malaysia]] aired in [[RCTI]] and [[TV3 (Malaysia)]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.idntimes.com/hype/throwback/hendria-1/5-film-dan-sinetron-cinta-laura-yang-pernah-jadi-paling-populer-c1c2|title=5 Film dan Sinetron Cinta Laura yang Pernah Jadi Paling Populer|trans-title=\nTop 5 Cinta Laura Movies and Soap operas that Ever Become Popular|language=Indonesian|publisher=idntimes.com|year=2018|accessdate=September 30, 2018}}</ref> Following her success, she released several songs ''You Say Aq'', ''Guardian Angel'', ''Cinta Atau Uang'', ''Tulalit'', ''Boomerang'' and ''Playlist'' for her second album ''Hollywood Dreams (2012)''.<ref name=\"auto24\">{{cite web|url=https://hype.my/2019/177106/interview-cinta-laura-kiehl-on-vida-acting-career-celebrating-xmas/|title=Interview: Cinta Laura Kiehl On \"Vida\", Acting Career & Celebrating X\u2019mas|language=English|publisher=HYPE MALAYSIA|year=2019|accessdate=November 20, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===2013\u2212present: International acting career and English album===\nIn 2013, she decided to move to [[Los Angeles]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://jakartaglobe.id/news/indonesian-actress-cinta-laura-lands-role-harry-potter-spin-off|title=Indonesian Actress Cinta Laura Lands Role in 'Harry Potter' Spin-Off|language=English|publisher=jakartaglobe.id|year=2015|accessdate=December 28, 2015}}</ref> In addition, Laura was offered to act in an [[Hollywood]]-produced movie ''[[After the Dark]]'' (2013), starring [[Bonnie Wright]] and [[James D\u2019Arcy]].<ref name=\"auto3\">{{cite web|url=http://www.fantasyfilmfest.com/filme/Philosophers.html|title=THE PHILOSOPHERS|language=English|publisher=fantasyfilmfest.com|accessdate=13 September 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130910054351/http://www.fantasyfilmfest.com/filme/Philosophers.html |archivedate=10 September 2013}}</ref><ref name=\"auto5\">{{cite web|url=http://www.phase4films.com/detail.aspx?projectId=77168dea-46d8-e211-8257-d4ae527c3b65|archive-url=https://archive.today/20131217171426/http://www.phase4films.com/detail.aspx?projectId=77168dea-46d8-e211-8257-d4ae527c3b65|url-status=dead|archive-date=December 17, 2013|title=After the Dark|language=English|accessdate=December 17, 2013}}</ref><ref name=\"auto6\">{{cite web|url=http://www.etonline.com/movies/143001_After_The_Dark_exclusive_clip/|title=An Apocalyptic Dilemma in 'After The Dark'|language=English|publisher=etonline.com|accessdate=February 7, 2014}}</ref> Laura work together with [[Grindstone Entertainment Group]],<ref name=\"auto18\">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/berlin-grindstone-picks-up-ninth-passenger-north-america-1085825|title=Berlin: Grindstone Picks Up 'Ninth Passenger' for North America (Exclusive)|language=English|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|year=2018|accessdate=February 17, 2018}}</ref> continuing her acting at ''[[The Ninth Passenger]]'' (2018) by [[Hollywood]] producer Corey Large.<ref name=\"auto8\">{{cite web|url=https://www.thejakartapost.com/life/2017/12/11/cinta-lauras-hollywood-films-to-premiere-next-year.html|title=Cinta Laura\u2019s Hollywood films to premiere next year|language=English|publisher=thejakartapost.com|year=2017|accessdate=December 11, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|author=Dave McNary|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/lionsgate-jesse-metcalfe-the-ninth-passenger-1201810393/ |title=Lionsgate Distributing Jesse Metcalfe\u2019s \u2018The Ninth Passenger\u2019|language=English|publisher=Variety.com|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2017-07-23}}</ref> She has also appeared on several [[Netflix]] [[LMN (TV channel)|Lifetime]] films,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.industry.co.id/read/5774/more-success-cinta-laura-starring-netflix-production-movies|title=More Success, Cinta Laura Starring Netflix Production Movies|language=English|publisher=industry.co.id|year=2018|accessdate=June 3, 2018}}</ref> such as ''Crazy For The Boys (2018)'',<ref name=\"auto23\">{{cite web|url=https://en.netralnews.com/news/currentnews/read/7561/cinta.laura.secures.main.role.in.hollywood.movie|title=Cinta Laura Secures Main Role in Hollywood Movie|language=English|publisher=netralnews.com|year=2017|accessdate=June 30, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"auto13\">{{cite web|url=https://www.thejakartapost.com/life/2017/07/07/cinta-laura-kiehl-to-star-in-american-musical-film.html|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl to star in American musical film|language=English|publisher=thejakartapost.com|year=2017|accessdate=July 7, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"auto15\">{{cite web|url=https://hot.detik.com/movie/d-3696131/intip-cinta-laura-syuting-film-hollywood-crazy-for-the-boys|title=Intip Cinta Laura Syuting Film Hollywood 'Crazy for the Boys'|trans-title=Let's Peek Cinta Laura Filming a New Hollywood film 'Crazy for the Boys'|language=Indonesian|publisher=hot.detik.com|year=2017|accessdate=October 27, 2017}}</ref> ''TAR (2018)'',<ref name=\"auto21\">{{cite web|url=https://kumparan.com/seleb-sensation/6-film-hollywood-yang-diperankan-cinta-laura-1538363151225635139|title=6 Film Hollywood yang Diperankan Cinta Laura|trans-title=Cinta laura Kiehl Playing on 6 Hollywood Movies|language=Indonesian|publisher=kumparan.com|year=2018|accessdate=October 1, 2018}}</ref> ''Goodnight (2018)''<ref name=\"auto21\"/> and ''The Nanny Is Watching (2018)''.<ref name=\"auto2\">{{cite web|url=https://www.earnthenecklace.com/lifetime-nanny-is-watching-cast-plot-premiere-date/|title=Lifetime\u2019s \"The Nanny Is Watching:\" Cast, Plot & Premiere Date|language=English|publisher=earnthenecklace.com|year=2018|accessdate=July 15, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"auto22\">{{cite web|url=https://www.thejakartapost.com/life/2018/06/05/cinta-laura-stars-in-netflix-film-nanny-surveillance.html|title=Cinta Laura Stars in Netflix Film, Nanny Surveillance|language=English|publisher=Jakarta Post|year=2018|accessdate=June 6, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"auto27\">{{cite web|url=https://vocal.media/geeks/lifetime-review-the-nanny-is-watching|title=Lifetime Review: 'The Nanny Is Watching'|language=English|publisher=vocal.media Reviews|year=2018|accessdate=June 6, 2018}}</ref> Laura won a ''\"Best Film Actress\"'' at the ''\"2019 Latino Film awards\"'', for the movie ''Goodnight'' (2018).<ref name=\"auto12\">{{cite web|url=https://longliveindonesia.com/best-actress-in-horror-film-award/|title=CINTA LAURA KIEHL WON THE BEST ACTRESS IN HORROR FILM AWARD|language=English|publisher=longliveindonesia.com|year=2019|accessdate=November 7, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"auto24\"/><ref name=\"auto28\">{{cite web|url=https://jogja.tribunnews.com/2019/11/05/cinta-laura-kiehl-raih-penghargaan-kategori-aktris-terbaik-di-latino-5th-annual-film-festival|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl Raih Penghargaan Kategori Aktris Terbaik di Latino 5th Annual Film Festival 2019|trans-title=\nCinta Laura Kiehl Won \"Best Film Actress\" Award in The 2019 Latino 5th Annual Film Festival|language=Indonesian|publisher=tribunnews.com|year=2019|accessdate=November 5, 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn 2019, Laura came back with her new English single ''Caliente''<ref name=\"auto4\">{{cite web|url=https://www.insertlive.com/film-dan-musik/20191126171411-25-69095/lirik-lagu-caliente--cinta-laura-kiehl|title=Song Lyrics of Caliente by Cinta Laura Kiehl|language=English|publisher=insertlive.com|year=2019|accessdate=November 26, 2019}}</ref> and ''Vida''<ref name=\"auto24\"/> after 7 years hiatus. She also starred in several Indonesian films such as ''Target (2018)'',<ref name=\"auto29\">{{cite web|url=https://www.liputan6.com/showbiz/read/3521902/main-film-raditya-dika-cinta-laura-dibayar-miliaran-rupiah|title=Main Film Raditya Dika, Cinta Laura Dibayar Miliaran Rupiah?|trans-title=Playing Raditya Dika Film, Cinta Laura, Paid Billions of Rupiah?|language=Indonesian|publisher=liputan 6|year=2018|accessdate=May 11, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"auto25\">{{cite web|url=https://www.jawapos.com/entertainment/music-movie/10/05/2018/alasan-cinta-laura-mau-terlibat-dalam-film-target/|title=Alasan Cinta Laura Mau Terlibat dalam Film Target|trans-title=Reasons Why Cinta Laura Wants To Be Involved in \"Target\" Film|language=Indonesian|publisher=liputan 6|year=2018|accessdate=May 10, 2018}}</ref> ''MatiAnak (2019)''<ref name=\"auto17\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hariandjakarta.com/musik-film/official-trailer-matianak|title=Official Trailer Film MatiAnak|language=English|publisher=hariandjakarta.com|year=2019|accessdate=February 22, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"auto9\">{{cite web|url=https://www.idntimes.com/hype/entertainment/rahmalia-nurida-1/5-fakta-film-matianak-aksi-perdana-cinta-laura-bintangi-film-horor-c1c2|title=5 Fakta Film 'MatiAnak', Aksi Perdana Cinta Laura Bintangi Film Horor|trans-title=5 Facts about the \"MatiAnak\" Film, Cinta Laura's First Starred on Horror Film|language=Indonesian|publisher=idntimes.com|year=2019|accessdate=March 19, 2019}}</ref> and ''Jeritan Malam'' (2019).<ref name=\"auto19\">{{cite web|url=https://today.line.me/id/pc/article/Cinta+Laura+Kiehl+reveals+strong+message+in+horror+film+Jeritan+Malam-YYypZj|title=Cinta Laura Kiehl reveals strong message in horror film 'Jeritan Malam'|language=English|publisher=today.line.me|year=2019|