ian film\n|[[comedy film]]\n|<ref name=\"auto29\"/><ref name=\"auto25\"/>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2019\n|''[[:id:MatiAnak|MatiAnak]]''\n|Ina\n|[[horror film]]\n|<ref name=\"auto17\"/><ref name=\"auto9\"/>\n|-\n|''[[:id:Jeritan Malam|Jeritan Malam]]''\n|Wulan\n|[[horror film]]\n|<ref name=\"auto19\"/><ref name=\"auto26\"/><ref name=\"auto16\"/><ref name=\"auto30\"/>\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| border=\"3\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\" <!-- Please do not change this -->\n|- style=\"background:#CCCCCC;\" align=\"center\"\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"background: LightSteelBlue;\"|Television drama\n|- style=\"background:#CCCCCC;\" align=\"center\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Production\n! Episodes\n! Ref.\n|-\n|2007\n|''[[Cinderella (Apakah Cinta Hanyalah Mimpi?)]]''\n|Cinta\n|[[MD Entertainment]]\n|310 Eps.\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://daman.co.id/cinta-laura-unveiled-exclusive/|title=Cinta Laura: Unveiled & Exclusive|language=English|publisher=daman.co.id|year=2010|accessdate=December 17, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://theparrot.co/2015/04/09/eurasians-take-show-business-by-storm-in-indonesia/|title=Cinta Laura: Unveiled & Exclusive|language=English|publisher=theparrot.co|year=2015|accessdate=April 9, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://kumparan.com/seleb-sensation/11-tahun-berlalu-apa-kabar-pemain-sinetron-cinderella-1533814983435187519|title=11 Tahun Berlalu, Apa Kabar Pemain Sinetron Cinderella?|trans-title=11 years have passed, how have been doing Cinderella soap opera actors?|language=Indonesian|publisher=kumparan.com|year=2018|accessdate=August 14, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2008\n|''Upik Abu dan Laura''\n|Laura\n|rowspan=2|Sinemart\n|110 Eps.\n|<ref name=\"auto24\"/>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2009\n|''Air Mata Cinta''\n|Cinta\n|53 Eps.\n|<ref name=\"auto24\"/>\n|}\n\n=== Variety show ===\n{| border=\"3\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"marg